data.description: This Delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in the Foothill Farms neighborhood awaits you. Some notable features are plantation shutters in the living room, granite kitchen, and some newer appliances. This property also includes a separate family and living room, a charming brick fireplace, low maintenance yard w/ a built in pool, and a generously sized lot with RV access. You'll appreciate the proximity to schools, parks, and shopping, as well as the easy access to the freeway. It's always a good time to become a homeowner, and you will be PROUD to call 5213 Diablo Dr - HOME.
